{"tid":1247172,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"1330前請政府回應大家訴求","createTime":"2019-06-21T04:19:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T04:24:32.000Z","uid":223933,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6a1fab022a7f1136f7dc4e6fa814d5b7ea81bc12","tid":1247172,"uid":223933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T04:19:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1300前請政府回應我哋四大訴求<br />\n一，釋放被捕人士<br />\n二，撤回送中修例<br />\n三，追究警方濫權<br />\n四，所有涉事高官問責下台<br />\n<br />\n否則行動將會升級</span></span><br />\n<br />\n請所有示威者去到警總附近<br />\n參考太陽花學運 <br />\n我哋將會衝入警察總部<br />\n佔領警總<br />\n如果政府依然不聞不問<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我們將不排除行動升級</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家聽我一言 如果再和理非<br />\n政府係唔撚會理我哋<br />\n<br />\n包圍政府部門 亦係冇撚用<br />\n所以我哋要做啲嘢逼政府面對<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋冇大台<br />\n所以我哋每一個都係大台<br />\n</span></span><br />\n唔好怕 永遠背後有人支持我哋 <br />\n而我哋將會係歷史中最偉大嘅一群<br />\n <br />\n利申：發緊夢大家好團結對抗黑暗帝國"},{"pid":"7e13601beb49842d922f8b2113897fb4013c7b68","tid":1247172,"uid":223933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T04:20:40.000Z","msg":"頭先on9開錯咗"},{"pid":"745280cb25cc0c86c1db7623db8703c3c9897c90","tid":1247172,"uid":223933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T04:21:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa37153986c5f2aec52f14f679568236626e40b1","tid":1247172,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e13601beb49842d922f8b2113897fb4013c7b68","tid":1247172,"uid":223933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T04:20:40.000Z","msg":"頭先on9開錯咗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T04:21:54.000Z","msg":"你而家都係On9<br />\n標題1330, 內文1300<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"162a81e5c67e88917f3bc3236ad33fba93466e25","tid":1247172,"uid":249965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T04:2